#### Recycling plastic waste: Our progress

In CY 2024, we successfully recycled 88% of the total
PET bottles consumed, exceeding the requirements
set by the Extended Producer Responsibility (EPR)
regulations of the CPCB. During the year, 206,682 MT
PET bottles were consumed, with 181,887 MT being
recycled within the same period, reinforcing our
commitment to sustainable waste management


##### Plastic waste recycling


