### Board of Directors

As at December 31, 2024, 5(Five) out of 10(Ten) Directors
on the Board were Independent Directors. At VBL, it is
our belief that an enlightened Board consciously creates
a culture of leadership to provide a long-term vision and
policy approach to improve the quality of governance.

The Board's actions and decisions are aligned with the
Company's best interests. The Board critically evaluates
the Company's strategic direction, management policies
and their effectiveness.

